Click Here for More GTeaLive Action! ► http://bit.ly/1Oo7KH9
Watch the 1st GTeaLive! ► https://bit.ly/2BU5yGh

It's a crazy time to be on YouTube right now. Another adpocalypse may be upon us, T Series beat out PewDiePie for 10 MINUTES, and now Shane Dawson might be the downfall of Chuck E Cheese? Plus Devotion, the game we've been playing the past few days, was pulled from Steam! Today, Steph and I are going to chat about all of this and more on GTeaLive!
